column4: NSLOCTEXT("[709C799D45CF03B72450B3B3B9D37524]", "06F6F70C49BF9B837877CD9B03764BC5", "Hey, are you the one building a city?")
NSLOCTEXT("[709C799D45CF03B72450B3B3B9D37524]", "2BF2E0374AC8EDE80135CEA9CA88B302", "Uh, you\'re real lucky to meet me.")
NSLOCTEXT("[709C799D45CF03B72450B3B3B9D37524]", "E7DE77094D81C5FBFA25FCAF653381B5", "I don\'t look it, but I\'m an Ultimate Digimon. If you beat me, I\'ll help you.")
NSLOCTEXT("[709C799D45CF03B72450B3B3B9D37524]", "A9C93AFF4BCDD42DC24959BDD53647EA", "Wow, I lost! Well, I\'ll see you in the city.")
NSLOCTEXT("[709C799D45CF03B72450B3B3B9D37524]", "FB50D3FF428604372221D6A2632AAFFB", "Oh, what a coward! Let\'s meet again!")
